It's not necessary to reopen the issue by yourself. You can just let us on about it and post the screenshot from the filter log like you did it via report tool.
As I can see, there is no referrer for the request and it might be the reason. Try this rule `||tacool.com^$badfilter` or you can disable it manually in the AdGuard Chinese through the editor.
@AdamWr please take a look at this.

The issue is caused by `Fanboy's Annoyances`.
Please add `otvet.mail.ru#@#.js-notifications-button` to the User Rules or disable this filter.
@ryanbr Could you please take a look?

